article.description: — Michael Ertel recorded 15 points as UAB romped past Charlotte 61-37 on Friday.
article.headline: Defense shines as UAB beats Charlotte 61-37
article.linkText: Defense shines as UAB beats Charlotte 61-37
article.story: CHARLOTTE, N.C -- — Michael Ertel recorded 15 points as UAB romped past Charlotte 61-37 on Friday. Jalen Benjamin added 10 points and Kassim Nicholson had 14 rebounds for UAB (10-1, 3-0 Conference USA). Tavin Lovan set career highs with eight assists and six steals. Brice Williams had 13 points and three blocks for the 49ers (5-6, 1-2), who turned it over 21 times and shot 31.6%. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
